data.description: Ready to move??? Seller is offering 5000.00 toward buyer's closing cost with accepted offer!!!!  This beautiful home features five bedrooms. 3.5 bath and a bonus room. Beautiful fireplace adorns the living room. Large formal dining room. This home is nestled in the heart of Broadway with a circle drive and a patio with covered porch just waiting for you to come and enjoy. Hardwood floors throughout the living and dining areas.  This home is a must see. Bonus room upstairs and a bedroom and a suite with a full bath. A lot of home to see.
